<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7845d570-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s558f"><num value="558f">§ 558f.</num><heading> Promotion of volunteer opportunities</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretaries shall promote volunteer opportunities in areas administered by the Secretaries.</p>
